{"tid":1840983,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦低音喇叭可唔可以駁AMP","createTime":"2020-01-25T05:48:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T08:29:32.000Z","uid":190224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e6b6ccea1594e7320daf2b81bc713faadc41f0a9","tid":1840983,"uid":190224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T05:48:14.000Z","msg":"我依家用緊電腦4.1 喇叭<br />\n想駁AMP 換埋喇叭搞個5.1 <br />\n不過不直有限, 可唔可以將依家用緊個低音喇叭駁AMP？<br />\n因為個低音喇叭係有源, 我驚會搞到D 野燒左<br />\n所以請教下大家先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21be25af7695cbb4aac62dc3e38817eeeec41f0","tid":1840983,"uid":190224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"019d81796036a25a01833c134f87e18db1ac2aaa","tid":1840983,"uid":7103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:52:29.000Z","msg":"你個低音係本身包埋amp?<br />\n<br />\n咁係得，將新amp嘅低音output signal一拆二做紅白線analog咁入隻低音度<br />\n<br />\n我自己都係咁做"},{"pid":"0cf399edc44571cb107e6a99b8e70270b3af0b0b","tid":1840983,"uid":190224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:35:28.000Z","msg":"我隻低音喇叭係有AMP, 可以駁埋D 迷你衛星喇叭<br />\n如果低音喇叭係3.5MM<br />\n係咪係新AMP 用條RCA 轉3.5MM 線就得?<br />\n定係要個新AMP 有PRE OUT 先得?<br />\n唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8f6d31882cf663684c96f251a52527c370b4a5","tid":1840983,"uid":81340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cf399edc44571cb107e6a99b8e70270b3af0b0b","tid":1840983,"uid":190224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:35:28.000Z","msg":"我隻低音喇叭係有AMP, 可以駁埋D 迷你衛星喇叭<br />\n如果低音喇叭係3.5MM<br />\n係咪係新AMP 用條RCA 轉3.5MM 線就得?<br />\n定係要個新AMP 有PRE OUT 先得?<br />\n唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:03:05.000Z","msg":"唔得<br />\nActive (有源） 喇叭input 係line level<br />\nAmp output係speaker level<br />\n基本上一定會整壞野<br />\n<br />\nPer amp 係另一樣野<br />\n普通咪嘅output 係mic level 比line level細大約20db<br />\n所以將mic level 轉 line level 係用pre amp (當然唔用pre amp , 直接將amp input gain 加大都得）"},{"pid":"3ba7fa1e7fb7dd621c7f639c79f5bb2e9f9f0a1b","tid":1840983,"uid":7103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cf399edc44571cb107e6a99b8e70270b3af0b0b","tid":1840983,"uid":190224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:35:28.000Z","msg":"我隻低音喇叭係有AMP, 可以駁埋D 迷你衛星喇叭<br />\n如果低音喇叭係3.5MM<br />\n係咪係新AMP 用條RCA 轉3.5MM 線就得?<br />\n定係要個新AMP 有PRE OUT 先得?<br />\n唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:33:44.000Z","msg":"要Pre out<br />\n<br />\n但我係駁入紅白line in，3.5mm唔知得唔得"},{"pid":"e6c690b7bec652134348827e4ddc83b16f175039","tid":1840983,"uid":7103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ba7fa1e7fb7dd621c7f639c79f5bb2e9f9f0a1b","tid":1840983,"uid":7103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cf399edc44571cb107e6a99b8e70270b3af0b0b","tid":1840983,"uid":190224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:35:28.000Z","msg":"我隻低音喇叭係有AMP, 可以駁埋D 迷你衛星喇叭<br />\n如果低音喇叭係3.5MM<br />\n係咪係新AMP 用條RCA 轉3.5MM 線就得?<br />\n定係要個新AMP 有PRE OUT 先得?<br />\n唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:33:44.000Z","msg":"要Pre out<br />\n<br />\n但我係駁入紅白line in，3.5mm唔知得唔得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:05:28.000Z","msg":"我google過，電腦喇叭3.5mm都係line level，應該冇問題<br />\n<br />\n有Pre out先可以新amp做前級，低音喇叭自帶隻amp做後級<br />\n冇pre out，line out都可以，但咁就要全部喇叭駁返重低音，做唔返5.1<br />\n<br />\n但千祈唔好speakers out插line in，如果唔係就好似上面講咁會燒機"},{"pid":"98a6bb72307bc248b18aa878c766488243cc1663","tid":1840983,"uid":190224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Su7vsAL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSu7vsAL.jpg&h=758c2c4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果依部AMP 係咪插PRE OUT 既SUBWOOFER 1 OR 2 就得?<br />\n同埋我見RCA 通常都係紅白線, 咁依個PRE OUT 應該插咩線<br />\n新手太多問題唔好介意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c011c03519600df077b4bfddf580759f8849dee4","tid":1840983,"uid":81340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:26:45.000Z","msg":"有冇你本身4.1嘅 model<br />\nAv amp  sub pre amp Rca&gt; mono 3.5 &gt; active subwoofer"},{"pid":"15eee0b1ea8fb3a996fcb6a561fb1179cae2d0ca","tid":1840983,"uid":81340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98a6bb72307bc248b18aa878c766488243cc1663","tid":1840983,"uid":190224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Su7vsAL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSu7vsAL.jpg&h=758c2c4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果依部AMP 係咪插PRE OUT 既SUBWOOFER 1 OR 2 就得?<br />\n同埋我見RCA 通常都係紅白線, 咁依個PRE OUT 應該插咩線<br />\n新手太多問題唔好介意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:28:33.000Z","msg":"如果買現成Rca &gt; 3.5 <br />\n應該用白色, 白色係去3.5嘅 tip"},{"pid":"c2260ea998d1da899cb3017f6b5aefe2d73f33a9","tid":1840983,"uid":190224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c011c03519600df077b4bfddf580759f8849dee4","tid":1840983,"uid":81340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:26:45.000Z","msg":"有冇你本身4.1嘅 model<br />\nAv amp  sub pre amp Rca&gt; mono 3.5 &gt; active subwoofer"},